{"id":121830,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/读《大萧条》偶感/","date":"2010-11-13T17:37:37Z","modified":"2010-11-13T17:37:37Z","title":"读《大萧条》偶感","content":"<p><p align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static1.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/5869d5a8t7450106f4c10&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static1.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/5869d5a8t7450106f4c10&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p align=\"center\"> </p>\n<p align=\"center\"> </p>\n<p align=\"center\">人啊，</p>\n<p align=\"center\">只有在黑夜里</p>\n<p align=\"center\">才看得见明灯</p>\n<p align=\"center\">一到白天</p>\n<p align=\"center\">眼里便没了太阳</p>\n<p align=\"center\"> </p>\n<p align=\"center\">所以古人说</p>\n<p align=\"center\">曲突徙薪无恩泽</p>\n<p align=\"center\">焦头烂额为上客</p>\n<p align=\"center\"> </p>\n<p align=\"center\">&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;-</p>\n<p align=\"center\">股民啊，</p>\n<p align=\"center\">只有到疯狗被打断脊梁</p>\n<p align=\"center\">才知道狂犬吠日的荒诞</p>\n<p align=\"center\">只是那时</p>\n<p align=\"center\">腰包已空，两腿已软</p>\n<p align=\"center\"> </p>\n<p align=\"center\">因此老巴说</p>\n<p align=\"center\">发财秘诀是保本</p>\n<p align=\"center\">保本保本还保本</p>\n<p align=\"center\"> </p>\n<p align=\"center\">&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;-</p>\n<p align=\"center\">有些人</p>\n<p align=\"center\">总觉得会比马克思看得还透</p>\n<p align=\"center\">有些股民</p>\n<p align=\"center\">总觉得会比索罗斯赚得还狠</p>\n<p align=\"center\"> </p>\n<p align=\"center\">于是上帝说</p>\n<p align=\"center\">如果没有了“黑周五”的冲击</p>\n<p align=\"center\">人就敢忘掉“大萧条”的滋味</p>\n<p align=\"center\"> </p></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[9203],"tags":[]}